OL,3,C'Brave' boy, 12, saves his family from
OL,4,Cdevastating house fire
OL,6,FThe quick actions of a twelve-year-old
OL,7,Fboy helped save his family from a
OL,8,Fdevastating electrical fire.
OL,10,FThe blaze broke out just before 9pm on
OL,11,FThursday at Millfield Close in Ashby-
OL,12,Fde-la-Zouch in North West
OL,13,FLeicestershire and destroyed their
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,FJennifer Drew, her mum Carol and her
OL,17,Fthree children - Nicholas (12),
OL,18,FElizabeth and Eleanor and their family
OL,19,Fcat were saved by Nicholas' quick
OL,20,Fthinking.
