OL,3,C'Brave' boy, 12, saves his family from
OL,4,Cdevastating house fire
OL,6,FHe heard the smoke alarm before
OL,7,Falerting those around him while
OL,8,Fdialling 999.
OL,10,FLeicestershire Fire and Rescue has
OL,11,Fpublicly praised Nicholas for his
OL,12,Fbravery: "He acted quickly and
OL,13,Fbravely... This is a perfect reminder
OL,14,Fof why smoke alarms are so important."
OL,16,FBoth of Jennifer's daughters,
OL,17,FElizabeth and Eleanor, are both
OL,18,Fseverely autistic and dependent on
OL,19,Fhaving their own safe, separate spaces
OL,20,Fto feel secure.
