OL,3,C'Brave' boy, 12, saves his family from
OL,4,Cdevastating house fire
OL,6,FEmma Dicken, Jennifer's sister, has
OL,7,Fset up the fundraiser to help replace
OL,8,Fessential items, rebuild the girls'
OL,9,Froutines and ease the burden as the
OL,10,Ffamily tries to get back on their feet.
OL,12,FIn a statement by Leicestershire
OL,13,FPolice, the force said: "A huge shout
OL,14,Fout goes to 12-year-old Nicholas, who
OL,15,Facted quickly and bravely.
OL,17,F"He alerted his entire family after
OL,18,Fhearing the smoke alarms and event
OL,19,Fcalled 999 to ask for the Fire
OL,20,FService."
